@• Validate the feeds with
  ‣ http://feedvalidator.org/check.cgi?url=http%3A//www.mirbsd.org/news.rss
  ‣ http://feedvalidator.org/check.cgi?url=http%3A//www.mirbsd.org/wlog-9.rss
